            </p>
            <p class="text-[18px] text-white max-sm:text-[14px]">
              Rank 1, 2020
            </p>
          </div>
        </Constrain>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex p-xl flex-col gap-l justify-center z-10 max-sm:p-r">
      <Constrain>
     <div class="flex items-center flex-col gap-l">
        <Heading
          first="Our"
          second="Objectives"
          subtitle="MISSION & VISION"
        ></Heading>
        <p class="text-2xl text-neutral-dark-grey max-w-[70ch] text-center">
          Insight Academy aims to direct the development of education to realize the immense nation building aptitudes and attitudes by utilizing the potential of aptly trained teachers. We believe education is not just a classroom affair, but it spreads over in myriad directions to provide learning in a child-friendly environment with no stress on confined syllabi or the examination.
        </p>
      </div>
  
    </Constrain>
  </div>
    <SlideShow />
  <!-- section -->
  <!-- section -->
    <div class="flex p-xl flex-col gap-l justify-center items-center  max-sm:p-r">
      <div class="w-full">
        <LeaderShipCTA />
      </div>
    </div>
  <!-- section -->
  <div class="flex p-xl flex-col gap-l justify-center items-center max-sm:p-r max-sm:gap-r">
    <div class="max-w-[1440px] ">
      <div class="flex container">

        <div class="flex w-full community-section rounded-[27px] rounded-br-none  bg-primary overflow-clip ">
          <div class="overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src={CommunityImage}
              alt="Image of community"
              class="basis-[25%] object-cover h-full" 
    
          />
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex  gap-[28px] flex-col w-full py-xl px-r basis-[70%] rounded-tr-[27px] card max-sm:gap-r">
            <Text type="h2" class="text-yellow font-bold max-sm:text-lg">
              Work with us
            </Text>
            <Text type="h1" class="text-white font-bold leading-[60px] max-md:leading-[40px]">
                Join the <br />
                Insight community
            </Text>
            <Text type='p' class="text-white">
              To view open career positions, <a href="" class="underline">click here</a>
            </Text>
          </div>
         
